quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Saad. Mi woo…óndirii Alqur'aana, jom waa."
  38,2,"Si ko woni, yeddu…ďe …ďe ngonii e townitaare e lurral !"
  38,3,"∆äuu…óii e gire …óen Min kalki, ado ma…ď…ďe, …ďe noddi faabo, kono tawi ko bonatno bonii."
  38,4,"∆Āe Ňčal…ói, nde jeertinoowo jiyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, arata …ďe. Yeddu…ďe …ďen mbi'i: ""Oo, ko bileejo keewu…óo fenaande,"
  38,5,"Kere o wa…óay dewetee…ói …óin, dewetee…óo gooto? Pellet, …óum ko hu'unde haawniinde non""."
  38,6,"Mbatu ma…ď…ďe ngun huccitiri wiide: ""Yehee, tabiton e dewetee…ói mon …óin. ∆äuum …óoo, ko hu'unde e…ď…ďanaande."
  38,7,"Min nanaali fii …óum, e diina sakkitiika kan. ∆äum wonaani, si wonaa ko fefkindaa."
  38,8,"Kere ko e makko JaŇčtoore nden jippotoo hakkunde amen?"" Si ko woni, …ďe ngonii e cikkitagol Jantoore am nden. Wurin, ko fii …ďe mee…óaali taho, lepte am …óen!"
  38,9,"Kaa …ďe njogiti ngaluuji yurmeende Joomi maa, poolu…óo, Dokko O?"
  38,10,"Kaa ko kam…ďe woodani laamagol kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji? Haray yo …ďe ∆īeenŇču …ďe ∆īawa!"
  38,11,"Ko …ďe konu hoyngu no, foolet e 'pe…óle …óen!"
  38,12,"Ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen njedduno, e Aadi'en e Fir'awna jom-peme,"
  38,13,"e Samuuda'en, e yim…ďe Luutu …ďe, e yim…ďe pitaaji …ďen; ko …ďeen ngoni fedde (fennu…ďe) …ďeen."
  38,14,"Kala …ďee wonaani, si wonaa o njeddi ii Nulaa…ďe …ďen. Lepte Am …óen jojji e ma…ď…ďe!"
  38,15,"∆Āee cabbaaki, si wonaa ha'acaango gooto, ngo alaa ruttorde."
  38,16,"∆Āe mbii': ""Joomi amen, yaccinan min ge…óal lepte amen, ado √Ďalaande hasboore nden""."
  38,17,"Mu√Ī√Īo e kon ko …ďe mbi'ata; annditaa jiyaa…óo Amen on, Daawuuda, joom doole. Ko o …óuu…óunoo…óo tuubugol."
  38,18,"Min eeltii pelle …óen, hi…óe cubbunhinoda e makko, ka kiikii…óe e ka bimmbi."
  38,19,"e colli …óin, hi…ói moo…ďindiraa, kala e majji no tuubana mo."
  38,20,"Min cemmbini laamu makko ngun, Min ye…ói mo Annabaaku e fasinteegal."
  38,21,"Hara kumpital wenoo…ďe …ďen arii maa, nde …ďe ∆īawunoo ka ganngunal !"
  38,22,"Nde …ďe naatunoo ka Daawuuda, o …óen∆īii …ďe. ∆Āe mbi'i: ""Wota a hul ! Ko wennju…ďe …ói…óo; go…ó…óo e amen too√Īii oya. √Ďaawir goonga hakkunde amen, wota a too√Ī, tinndinaa min e laawol Pocciingol ngol."
  38,23,"Oo ko musi…ó…óo am: homo jogii baali cappan…óe jeenay e jeenay, miin mi…óo jogii baalii gootii. O wi'i: ""Henndinam ngii""; o foolimi e yeewtere."
  38,24,"O maaki: ""Pellet, o too√Īirii ma la…ďndagol baalii maa ngii, wa…ótugol e baali makko …óin"". ∆äuu…óii ko hawtu…ďe too√Īindirta hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, si wonaa …ďen gooŇč…óiin…ďe, …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īu…ói - …ďen non no fan…ói. - Daawuuda felliti, won'de Min njarribike mo. O imsinanii Joomi makko, o suuyiri sujjugol, o tuubi."
  38,25,"Min njaafanii mo …óum. Pellet non, hino woodani mo ko amen, …ďadal e mo∆ī∆īude ruttorde."
  38,26,"Eey ma Daawuuda, Min mba…óii ma lomto ka leydi. √Ďaawir goonga hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen, wota a jokku mbelee…óe, sakko …óe majjine e laawol Allah ngol"". Pellet, …ďen majjoo…ďe e laawol Allah ngol, hino woodani …ďe lepte tii…óu…óe, sabu ko …ďe yejjitiri kon, √Ďalaande hasboore nden."
  38,27,"Min tagiraali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, meere. ∆äum ko sikke yeddu…ďe …ďen. Bone woodanii …ďen yeddu…ďe, e Yiite ngeen!"
  38,28,"Ka Min mb…óay …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi, wano bonnoo…ďe …ďen ka hoore leydi? Kaa Min mba…óay gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen, wano faajiree…ďe …ďeen?"
  38,29,"Ko deftere barkinaande, woni ko Min njippini e maa…óa, fii no …ďe taskora aayeeje mayre, e ko joomiraa…ďe haqqille …ďen mbaajitora."
  38,30,"Min nje…ói Daawuuda Sulaymaana, - jiyaa…óo mo∆ī∆īo - Ko o …óuu…óu…óo tuubugol-ruttoo."
  38,31,"JaŇčto nde o hollanoo kiikii…óe, pucci yoo…óu…ói yaawu…ói,"
  38,32,"o maaki: ""Min …ďurnorii jo…ógol jawdi, dii ko mi jaŇčtotoo Joomi am kon, haa [na'ange] ngen mutoyii."
  38,33,"Nduttee kam …ói"". O woni e sodugol …ói ka taape e ka daa…óe."
  38,34,"Goo…óii Min njarribike Sulaymaana, Min mbernii e jullere makko nden …ďanndu. refti o tuubi."
  38,35,"O maaki: ""Joomi am, haforanam, ye…óaa kam laamu, ngu heertantaako go…ó…óo goo, …ďaawo am. Pellet, ko an woni je…óoowo On""."
  38,36,"Min eeltani mo henndu ndun, tawi hindu wifira e sago makko, neweende, nokku kala to o yi…ói."
  38,37,"E seytanuuji …óiin, mahaynoo…ói e mutaynoo…ói."
  38,38,"Go…ó…ói …ói, ko dummbaa…ói e peŇč…óe."
  38,39,"""∆äuum ko dokkal Amen. Okkitir, maa njogitoraa ko aldaa e la…ďnditoreede""."
  38,40,"Ko pellet, hino woodani mo ka amen, …ďadal e mo∆ī∆īude ruttorde."
  38,41,"JaŇčto kadi jiyaa…óo Amen on Ayyuuba, nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, won'de : ""Seytaane memirii lam tampere e muuseendi""."
  38,42,"[Allah wi'ani mo]: ""Latir tunndawal maa ngal [ka leydi]: ∆äam …óoo, ko lootor…óam, …ďuu…ď…óam e njaram""."
  38,43,"Min nje…ói mo …ďeynguure makko nden, e yeru ma…ď…ďe tawti …ďe, yurmeende immorde e amen, e waaju wonan'de mar…ďe haqqille …ďen."
  38,44,"""Nanngir sookewo maa ngon, tamere hu…óo, piyiraa …óum [cuddii…óo maa on], fii wata a firtu (woondoore nden)"". Min tawu mo, mu√Ī√Īii…óo. O mo∆ī∆īii jiyaa…óo. Pellet, ko o …óuu…óu…óo tuubugol-ruttoo."
  38,45,"JaŇčto kadi, jiyaa…ďe Amen …ďen, Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba, joomiraa…ďe semmbe e yi'an…óe."
  38,46,"Min keertinanii …ďe heertinannde, annditugol galle (laakara) …óen."
  38,47,"E kadi …ďee ka amen, ko jiyaa…ďe e su…ďaa…ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ďe su…ďaa…ďe."
  38,48,"JaŇčto kadi Ismaa'iila, e Yuusa'u, e Zal-Kifli, kala ma…ď…ďe, ko jiyaa…ďe e su…ďaa…ďe."
  38,49,"∆äum ko waaju. Ko pellet, hino woodani gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen, ruttorde mo∆ī∆īunde."
  38,50,"∆äuum ko Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal, …ói …ďe udditanaa dame mum,"
  38,51,"hara ko …ďe so…ď…ďindii …ďe ton, he…ďe nodda ton muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói e njaram."
  38,52,"Hino woodani …ďe (ton): ra…ď…ďu…ďe ndaar…óe, goree…ďe."
  38,53,"Ko …óum woni ko poda…óon, fii √Ďalaande hasboore ndeen."
  38,54,"Pellet, …óum ko arsike amen, gasugol alanaa mo."
  38,55,"∆äuum, [ko njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe]. Pellet, hino woodani kadi bew…ďe …ďeen, ko …ďuri bonnde e ruttorde,"
  38,56,"woni Jahannama, nge …ďe naatoyta. Nge bonii nda…ó…óudi!"
  38,57,"∆äuum, ko yo …ďe mee…ó: ko fatata, e ∆īi∆ī∆īiri,"
  38,58,"Wo…ď…ďe …ďen, nanndu…óe e majje, ko nooneeji."
  38,59,"E hino dental naatiroyat ngal doole e mon, toolii alanaa …ďe; tawde ko …ďe naatoo…ďe Yiite !"
  38,60,"∆Āeen mbia: bismilla alanaa mon, ko onon ndefi min …óum"". Nge bonii √Īii…ďirde."
  38,61,"∆Āe mbi'a: ""Joomi amen, defu…óo min …óuim on, …ďeydan mo leptte cowalle ka Yiite""."
  38,62,"∆Āeya mbi'i: ""Ko ha…ói men jiugol wor…ďe, …ďe min limtaynoo e boon…ďe …ďen?"
  38,63,"Hara min njogitorno …ďe toon jalnori, kaa ko gite (amen) yawti …ďe?"""
  38,64,"Pellet, ka goonga, ko …óuum woni yeddondiral yim…ďe Yiite …ďeen."
  38,65,"Maaku: ""Anndee ko mi jeertinoowo. Dewetee…óo woo alaa, si wonaa Allah Gooto, poolu…óo On,"
  38,66,"Jey…óo kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde …óin …ói…ói, poolu…óo, kaforoowo On""."
  38,67,"Maaku: ""(ndee Alqur'aanaare), ko nde kabaaru maw…óo,"
  38,68,"kono ho…óon …óuurnii …óum."
  38,69,"Ganndal alanaano kam, e fii mbatu ngun dowrowu, tuma nde …ďe wee√Īidaynoo."
  38,70,"Wahayinaaka e am, si wanaa won'de min on, ko mi jeertinoowo …ďanngina""."
  38,71,"JaŇčto nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: ""Min mi tagiroowo …ďanndiŇčke, immorde loopal."
  38,72,"si mi fotindirii mo, Mi wuttii e makko ruuhu am on, haray suuyanee mo cujjon""."
  38,73,"Malaa'ika'en fof cujji …ďe denndaangal."
  38,74,"si wonaa Ibuliisa, o mawnintinii, o woni jiyaa…óo e yeddu…ďe …ďen."
  38,75,"(Allah) daali: ""eey ma yo Ibuliisa, ko ha…óu maa sujjangol ko Mi tagiri juu…óe am? A mawnintini kaa a jeya e townitii…ďe …ďeen?"""
  38,76,"O wi'i: ""Ko min …ďuri mo mo∆ī∆īude. A tagirii lam e yiite, A tagirii mo kaŇčko e loopal""."
  38,77,"O daali: ""Yaltu ton, aan, ko a diiwaa…óo;"
  38,78,"pellet, kuddi sm ndin fawike ma haa √Ďande njo…ďdi diina""."
  38,79,"(Ibuliisa) wi'i : ""Joomi am, nee…ďnitanam, haa √Īande nde …ďe immintintee""."
  38,80,"O daali: ""A jeyaama e nee…ďnitantee…ďe …ďen,"
  38,81,"haa e √Īalaande happu ganndaa…óo""."
  38,82,"O wi'i: ""Mi woo…óndirii mawngu maa ngun ! Ma mi bewnu…ďe fof ma…ď…ďe,"
  38,83,"si wonaa jiyaa…ďe Maa, la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe""."
  38,84,"(Allah) daali: ""Mi woo…óndirii goonga, ko goonga mi wowlata,"
  38,85,"ma Mi hebbinire Jahannama, e …ďen jokku…ďe ma fof e ma…ď…ďe""."
  38,86,"Maaku: ""Mi la…ďndaaki on njo…ďdi e fii …óum; mi wonaali jeyaa…óo e sincoo…ďe(deftatoobe)."
  38,87,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] wonaani, si wonaa waaju tageefo ngon."
  38,88,"Ma on nganndu (fii) kabaaru mayre, ko nee…ďaa !""."
